'''Ajjed''' neɣ '''asɣan''' d tagrumma n wayen ttamnen medden d leɛwayed i teddun yid-sen.

== [[Tudayt]] ==
Tudayt d ajjed amezwaru ideg ttamnen medden belli yella yiwen Yakuc kan. Isem-is s [[tɛebrit]] : Yehweh. Udayen ur nezmir ara ad neṭqen isem-agi axaṭer ɣur-sen ḥram. Yakuc g tudayt yesɛa lemluk i t-ttɛawanen, yuzen rruṣel ɣur medden akken ad ttamnen yis-es. Yahvé yextar agdud : agdud n israyil akken ad necren awal n yakuc.

== [[Tamasiḥit]] ==
G Tamasiḥit, Yakuc d yiwen, iṣubb ɣer medden s wedmaw n bnadem : [[Ɛisa]].

== [[Islam|Lislam]] ==
G lislam, Yakuc d yiwen meɛna ur iṣubb ara, Ɛisa ɣur inselmen d nnbi kan.


